name: Cache (2018) Box Press Robusto
additionalNotes:
Cached was released in 2014 in a single 5 x 52 size. It came in a 25-count box with 20 cigars on top in a round 5 x 52 size and five cigars in the bottom in a box-pressed 5 x 52 shape.

Halfwheel- Like the 2014 release, the new versions (2018) use a Mexican San Andrés wrapper over a Nicaraguan binder and Nicaraguan fillers. Production is once again being handled by Tabacos Valle de Jalapa S.A. (TABSA) in Estelí, Nicaragua.
